<h3>Package shipping from:</h3>
<p><%= @order.shipping_from.address %></p>

<h3>Package shipping to:</h3>
<p><%= @order.shipping_to.address %></p>

<h3>Package owner:</h3>
<p><%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %></p>

<h3>Comments on this owner:</h3>
<% @user.comments.each do |comment| %>
	<ul>
	<li><%= comment.comment %> - <%= User.find(comment.commentor_id).first_name %></li>
	</ul>
<% end %>

<h3>Total packages sent by owner prior to this package:</h3>
<p><%= @user.total_sent %></p>

<h3>Have any questions you'd like to ask the owner?</h3>
<p>If you have any questions or comments that you'd like to communicate to the owner, fill out the box below and we'll email him.</p>

<%= form_tag "/talk_to_senders" do %>
	<%= text_field_tag :questions_or_comments_to_sender %>
	<%= submit_tag "send questions or/and comments" %>
	<%= hidden_field_tag :order_id, @order.id %>
<% end %>

<p>Otherwise, if you're ready to commit to taking this package, hit COMMMIT!!

<br>

Upon hitting COMMIT we'll notify the owner that you are ready to take his package. As soon as he agrees we'll give you his addresses and you'll be on your way!</p>

<%= form_tag "/talk_to_senders/#{@order.id}", :method => :patch do %>
	<%= submit_tag "COMMIT" %>
<% end %>